### **4. 24_StreamPlotMonitor**  
**Description:**  
Live-plotting tool to visualize real-time numeric input on a chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamPlotMonitor - Real-Time Chart Visualizer

StreamPlotMonitor builds animated graphs from numeric data streams like sensors, APIs, or simulations.

## Features
- Live Matplotlib plot  
- Smooth line updates  
- CLI integration  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_StreamPlotMonitor.git
cd 24_StreamPlotMonitor
python visualize.py
